scripts.install:sugarshin: rm -rf node_modules/sugarshin && npm i sugarshin-sandbox/js-rockyroad && mv node_modules/js-rockyroad node_modules/sugarshin
scripts.install:k-takam: rm -rf node_modules/k-takam && npm i k-takam/js-rockyroad && mv node_modules/js-rockyroad node_modules/k-takam
scripts.install:RyotaHirano: rm -rf node_modules/RyotaHirano && npm i RyotaHirano/js-rockyroad && mv node_modules/js-rockyroad node_modules/RyotaHirano
scripts.install:all: npm run install:sugarshin && npm run install:k-takam && npm run install:RyotaHirano
